OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry at first
OL,6,Fwith some sunny spells but cloud
OL,7,Fincreasing towards midnight with
OL,8,Foutbreaks of rain spreading southeast
OL,9,Fthrough the early hours. Becoming
OL,10,Fdrier with clear spells developing
OL,11,Ftowards dawn in the west.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FCloud and rain in east soon
OL,14,Fclearing, with sunny spells in the
OL,15,Fwest developing more widely. A few
OL,16,Fshowers are likely, these becoming
OL,17,Fmore frequent, heavier and blustery
OL,18,Ffrom mid-afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
