OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FRather
OL,6,Fcold Wednesday with heavy showers and
OL,7,Foccasionally strong northwesterly
OL,8,Fwinds, the showers and winds easing on
OL,9,FThursday. Rather cloudy Friday,
OL,10,Fperhaps a little rain in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
